Music-Barrel  0.9 alpha
=======================

Music Juke box for Raspberry Pi

1. Installation
---------------

An installation package is coming, however for now just follow
the guide to install app server on Raspberry Pi
http://tjws.sourceforge.net/arch-raspi-java8.html
And then drop the .war file in webapps deploy directory.

Point your desktop or mobile browser to http://raspberrypi/music-barrel
Visit Setting barrel first to initialize database schema.


2. Sources access
-----------------

Visit https://github.com/drogatkin/music-barrel
